    "19102305": {
      "title": "Biological determinants of endocrine resistance in breast cancer",
      "abstract": "The efficacy of endocrine therapies (such as tamoxifen) in breast cancer is limited by intrinsic and acquired therapeutic resistance. What do we know about the genetic lesions and molecular processes that determine endocrine resistance in the clinic, and how can we use this to improve therapy?"
    }
